{
  "levelId": "block-05",
  "chapterId": "block-05",
  "worldId": "block",
  "title": "遗迹图书馆：找出旧地图",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "ruins",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/block/block-05.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "遗迹图书馆的书架由石头方块砌成。一本旧地图藏在会发光的书后面。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是遗迹图书馆。我们先把“找出旧地图”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到方块碰撞的声音，新的建造点就在前面。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先找稳固的方块，再一步一步搭出安全的路线。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "collect",
          "prompt": "从书架上取下标着星光的旧地图。",
          "character": "cave_keeper",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "取下蓝边地图",
              "feedback": "地图展开，露出了地下城最深处。"
            },
            {
              "label": "翻开厚故事书",
              "feedback": "书里夹着一枚闪亮的书签。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，取下蓝边地图让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "方块放稳后，藏在墙后的通道露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这段通道接到村子的道路上，伙伴们就能一起通过。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这块特别的方块，它会成为下一座建筑的起点。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "一本书像一扇门，打开它，就能看见新的地方。",
          "character": "cave_keeper",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
